          "Hadith.1797 - It is narrated by Dawud al-Raqqi from Abu Abdullah (Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as)), Imam (as) said:\n\"Breaking your fast at your brother's home is better than fasting seventy or even ninety times.\""
